data.description: Not your cookie cutter home! This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home boasts a deep 3 car garage, and versatile bonus room. The interior features vaulted ceilings, brand new carpet, coffered ceilings in the primary bedroom, wood accent walls, abundant storage.  Situated in a quiet cul-de-sac, this residence combines style and comfort for an ideal living space.  Love to entertain or watch the seasons change? The large stamped concrete covered patio is equipped for year round outdoor enjoyment with built-in patio lights, and blue tooth sound system. Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, Lake Lowell and RedHawk Public Golf Course.
